{"tid":1849552,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"［官府開倉］直擊政府倉庫存囤積最少90箱N95口罩 男子聞記者查問即大力關門","createTime":"2020-01-29T06:18:33.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-30T06:21:09.000Z","uid":203207,"like":267,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":62,"replies":[{"pid":"8892512c5ec2650f6592686aec2339049a250792","tid":1849552,"uid":203207,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-29T06:18:33.000Z","msg":"政府高官連日來都不肯呼籲市民戴口罩，特首林鄭月娥昨更惺惺作態稱會向中國國務院求助，要求供應國產口罩，但旋即被網民踢爆政府其實有逾億個口罩存貨。有讀者向《蘋果》爆料，指衞生署的倉庫仍有大量口罩封存，尚待出貨。記者上門叩門查詢，一名男子開門，聽罷記者問「呢度係唔係衞生署嘅口罩倉？」即大力關門，拒作回應。而就在他開門的數秒間，《蘋果》拍攝到倉內最少有2大塊卡板，每塊卡板擺放著最少45箱貨物；箱上的標籤列明「2130 N95 Respirator」，並有品牌「GERSON」標誌，相信是N95 口罩。<br />\n該大廈保安向記者承認，該貨倉隸屬衞生署，「積落好多口罩⋯⋯分啲畀市民，我就唔使周圍撲口罩喇！」沒戴口罩的他說。<br />\n<br />\n查冊顯示，被指為衞生署口罩倉的工廠單位由冠榮有限公司持有，2013年起被政府全層租用，目前租約至2020年11月，每月租金10萬元。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200126/MCI5O4GN77UVLDR73B4WSEXFP4/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200126%2FMCI5O4GN77UVLDR73B4WSEXFP4%2F&d=5FuYkWQ3QtYmval6ncx7JmZ69rz5%2BYz%2FKt%2FQ7ZoV0Dw%3D&h=ac90ace9\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200126%2FMCI5O4GN77UVLDR73B4WSEXFP4%2F&h=c3efd43d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200126/MCI5O4GN77UVLDR73B4WSEXFP4/</a><br />\n<br />\n樓下開始多人<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"712397902dc84820c324adb34eb76c8efe913b9e","tid":1849552,"uid":5502,"like":40,"dislike":3,"score":37,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2020-01-29T06:19:07.000Z","msg":"攻入去再派？"},{"pid":"915026cc9e4f20765187a48aa4015dde07a5c905","tid":1849552,"uid":38904,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"quote":{"pid":"712397902dc84820c324adb34eb76c8efe913b9e","tid":1849552,"uid":5502,"like":40,"dislike":3,"score":37,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2020-01-29T06:19:07.000Z","msg":"攻入去再派？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-29T06:20:42.000Z","msg":"解決一切問題<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/agree2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"40ecaad28371062b3b84fb007b8630fb25751020","tid":1849552,"uid":76310,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-29T06:21:42.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://petitions.whitehouse.gov/petition/appeal-add-genuine-dual-universal-suffrage-hong-kong-part-phase-2-agreement-between-us-and-china\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpetitions.whitehouse.gov%2Fpetition%2Fappeal-add-genuine-dual-universal-suffrage-hong-kong-part-phase-2-agreement-between-us-and-china&d=5FuYkWQ3QtYmval6ncx7JmZ69rz5%2BYz%2FKt%2FQ7ZoV0Dw%3D&h=9bae31c9\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://petitions.whitehouse.gov/petition/appeal-add-genuine-dual-universal-suffrage-hong-kong-part-phase-2-agreement-between-us-and-china</a><br />\n要求香港真雙普選作為第二階段中美貿易協議一部份<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n呢度簽得七七八八<br />\n麻煩fb tg發出去搵新客源簽"},{"pid":"e3ef4899c1631f75c4bd611301b2b3556207be2d","tid":1849552,"uid":203207,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-29T06:21:45.000Z","msg":"要係黑狗黎之前散水喎"},{"pid":"bd72112efafb04d7890e25e026f7da2c33997d56","tid":1849552,"uid":158613,"like":19,"dislike":0,"score":19,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-29T06:22:58.000Z","msg":"無口罩，又強制d人去外出逼車返工<br />\n係唔係要趕香港人入絕路？"},{"pid":"76e094380e8607fe05712974fd86f83e451411c3","tid":1849552,"uid":203207,"like":27,"dislike":0,"score":27,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-29T06:23:08.000Z","msg":"與其排屈臣氏 阿布<br />\n何不排政府倉？"},{"pid":"7ccb839a2799c2e61b88a84f89426da16f693f00","tid":1849552,"uid":9394,"like":79,"dislike":6,"score":73,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2020-01-29T06:23:57.000Z","msg":"冷靜啲 <br />\n醫護確實係有需要用咁多<br />\n目標應該係逼政府拎呢堆n95派比前線醫護/救護<br />\n唔好比啲高層<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5b11e1c7c057c92dc2edab9ecab6636c5555cc0e","tid":1849552,"uid":203207,"like":13,"dislike":4,"score":9,"quote":{"pid":"7ccb839a2799c2e61b88a84f89426da16f693f00","tid":1849552,"uid":9394,"like":79,"dislike":6,"score":73,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2020-01-29T06:23:57.000Z","msg":"冷靜啲 <br />\n醫護確實係有需要用咁多<br />\n目標應該係逼政府拎呢堆n95派比前線醫護/救護<br />\n唔好比啲高層<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-01-29T06:25:05.000Z","msg":"如果醫護都唔夠罩 咪多個誘因/藉口罷工囉"},{"pid":"ae54b3616348000751302f222b63beffdacf2d11","tid":1849552,"uid":14918,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-01-29T06:25:12.000Z","msg":"地址: 冠華鏡廠第三工業大廈"},{"pid":"07071c4ac44cc89bfde799370ff28ea9b61315fe","tid":1849552,"uid":41818,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-29T06:26:06.000Z","msg":"領導先用"},{"pid":"1f510bcbe6f95533aa0295e94c82cba8e0df9451","tid":1849552,"uid":203207,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ae54b3616348000751302f222b63beffdacf2d11","tid":1849552,"uid":14918,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-01-29T06:25:12.000Z","msg":"地址: 冠華鏡廠第三工業大廈"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-29T06:26:13.000Z","msg":"傳出去"},{"pid":"c1b166bd355ffea6660fc31aa4b9f05c18bf139a","tid":1849552,"uid":150610,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-29T06:26:23.000Z","msg":"屌佢老母，香港人就排到閪咁，口罩全部送返大陸，點撚樣防疫<br />\n英文反應幾撚快，民選即係民選"},{"pid":"45958a9e3058d7528af485181f9cf954f5d4b696","tid":1849552,"uid":28833,"like":9,"dislike":9,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-29T06:26:29.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"6cd92cf2e098f32458b5544c23b995e8ef9fb348","tid":1849552,"uid":45983,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-29T06:26:44.000Z","msg":"勇武加油"},{"pid":"ac7dfd4924db8ccc650e804ac57b1712c18621b0","tid":1849552,"uid":344033,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-29T06:27:20.000Z","msg":"手足裝備抗沙士：護目鏡 非常重要！分析文！大力推！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1845419\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1845419</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/112357283631796/posts/117867026414155/?d=n\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F112357283631796%2Fposts%2F117867026414155%2F%3Fd%3Dn&d=5FuYkWQ3QtYmval6ncx7JmZ69rz5%2BYz%2FKt%2FQ7ZoV0Dw%3D&h=cb3fe50f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/112357283631796/posts/117867026414155/?d=n</a><br />\n<br />\n手足裝備抗沙士：護目鏡<br />\n整體分析：<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/112357283631796/posts/116690396531818/?d=n\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F112357283631796%2Fposts%2F116690396531818%2F%3Fd%3Dn&d=5FuYkWQ3QtYmval6ncx7JmZ69rz5%2BYz%2FKt%2FQ7ZoV0Dw%3D&h=11de995a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/112357283631796/posts/116690396531818/?d=n</a><br />\n<br />\n個別分析：<br />\n護目鏡：<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1845419\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1845419</a><br />\n防毒面具/濾罐：<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1848447\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1848447</a><br />\n<br />\n&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;<br />\n首選：Sellstrom S80225/S80226 Wildland Fire Goggles （戴眼鏡都用得）<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.amazon.com/Sellstrom-Wildland-Goggles-Non-Vented-Anti-Fog/dp/B07DJVPL9Q\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.amazon.com%2FSellstrom-Wildland-Goggles-Non-Vented-Anti-Fog%2Fdp%2FB07DJVPL9Q&d=5FuYkWQ3QtYmval6ncx7JmZ69rz5%2BYz%2FKt%2FQ7ZoV0Dw%3D&h=e395f62e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.amazon.com/Sellstrom-Wildland-Goggles-Non-Vented-Anti-Fog/dp/B07DJVPL9Q</a><br />\n<br />\nSellstrom 依款眼罩，上年九月果陣，已經係前線手足標準裝備，有手足認證，包保放心！其中，依款眼罩有兩大特點。<br />\n<br />\n第一，依款眼罩寫明係 non-vented，即係氣密。戴左之後，基本上就阻隔左外面嘅空氣進入眼罩，所以擋到TG，亦都擋到帶病毒嘅飛沫同空氣，乜春都入唔到眼。依個亦都係佢可以俾美國消防員救山火果陣用嘅原因。氣密係眼罩第一重要條件，如果唔係氣密，病毒同TG都可以經眼罩邊位入眼，大陸衛健委都講明病毒傳染性不斷上升，美國有教授都講左武漢沙士嘅reproductive rate 高過曬佢見過佢嘅病毒，證明今次係非常嚴重，必須要用高規格嘅產品保護自己！<br />\n<br />\n第二，依款眼罩經過 ANSI Z87+ 嘅驗證，保護性極高！<br />\nANSI Z87+嘅定義如下：<br />\n&lsquo;Each product must go through rigorous third-party testing which simulates hazards such as impact by flying objects and debris, high mass impact, and sharp object penetration. In each testing scenario, the lenses and frame must stay intact to pass&rsquo;<br />\n根據網上一個對ANSI Z87+ 眼罩嘅測試，散彈槍都射佢唔穿，所以ANSI Z87+ 嘅standard 係非常高，亦都只有依種眼罩嘅保護性先可以保護前線免受橡膠子彈同布袋彈威脅。<br />\n<br />\n但係有巴打指出部份面型有機會有gap, 建議如果屋企多人買多幾種唔同牌子試下<br />\n&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;<br />\n次選：<br />\nPyramex CAPSTONE (G504DT或其他型號）<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.amazon.com/Pyramex-Capstone-Direct-Indirect-Anti-Fog/dp/B003UUEW88\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.amazon.com%2FPyramex-Capstone-Direct-Indirect-Anti-Fog%2Fdp%2FB003UUEW88&d=5FuYkWQ3QtYmval6ncx7JmZ69rz5%2BYz%2FKt%2FQ7ZoV0Dw%3D&h=f86ea990\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.amazon.com/Pyramex-Capstone-Direct-Indirect-Anti-Fog/dp/B003UUEW88</a><br />\n<br />\n第一，依款眼罩有氣密帽，應該同樣做到氣密效果，但係因為佢嘅氣密帽可以拆卸，多左個連接位，所以氣密保護性會低小小（始終多個連接位就多個出錯機<br />\n會）。（巴打指出Pyramex Capstone 只係indirect vent，唔係non-vented） <br />\n如果有心改，可以買熱熔膠封透氣孔<br />\n第二，依款眼罩經過D3 測試，證實可以防水滴同化學劑嘅飛淺，理論上有足夠防水性能。<br />\n第三，依款眼罩經過MIL-PRF 32432 美軍標準測試，對子彈衝擊力有一定防禦。<br />\n<br />\nUber Ultravision Gas Goggle <br />\n<a href=\"https://www.uvex-safety.com/en/products/safety-glasses/6712/uvex-ultravision-wide-vision-goggle/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.uvex-safety.com%2Fen%2Fproducts%2Fsafety-glasses%2F6712%2Fuvex-ultravision-wide-vision-goggle%2F&d=5FuYkWQ3QtYmval6ncx7JmZ69rz5%2BYz%2FKt%2FQ7ZoV0Dw%3D&h=95a83a7f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.uvex-safety.com/en/products/safety-glasses/6712/uvex-ultravision-wide-vision-goggle/</a><br />\n<br />\n熱門牌子眼罩比人掃左好多，最近有手足推介依款uvex 眼罩。<br />\n第一，佢寫明係gas-tight， 同埋 no ventilation, 所以同樣做到non-vented 效果。<br />\n第二，佢過左歐盟嘅EN166, EN170 測試，寫明可以防fine dust particle （smaller than 5 micron), 可防超細粒子，令人用得比較放心，同埋EN166 嘅test，對防衝擊力一定有一定要求，所以亦適合發夢<br />\n第三，官網寫話戴眼鏡都用得<br />\n<br />\n3M 1621 護目鏡<br />\n<br />\n雖然唔係完全氣密，但係過左D3 test 同 ANSI Z87.1 （冇過plus 果個），對飛沫有一定預防能力，依幾日試過，除左大霧啲之外其他都ok, 包得幾好，重點係好便，五金舖$20-30 就有，性價比最高！<br />\n巴打指出大霧，唔適合返工<br />\n<br />\n泳鏡（仲易買過平光鏡）<br />\n<br />\n泳鏡顧名思義，就係for 遊水，氣密效果有一定嘅保證，同埋求其一間運動鋪都可以買到，買近視鏡嘅話眼睛都唔洗戴，幾十蚊就有，保護性一定好過平光鏡，不過如果係講嘢都要除口罩，放屁要除褲，戴左帽可能腦都用唔到嘅人，可能佢戴左就會睇唔野。<br />\n<br />\n&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;<br />\n8.5 最新護目鏡實測 條帶戴高D 鼻位GAP就會消失!!! &amp; 前線超過400位豬嘴實測<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1411916\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1411916</a><br />\n<br />\n大家幫幫手，like &amp; share 等多啲人睇到！<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/dE5IweYn3T4\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FdE5IweYn3T4&d=5FuYkWQ3QtYmval6ncx7JmZ69rz5%2BYz%2FKt%2FQ7ZoV0Dw%3D&h=13d07af2\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/dE5IweYn3T4</a><br />\n清洗參考<br />\n<br />\n建議清潔步驟<br />\n1.番到屋企，洗手<br />\n2.唔好除眼罩住，用火酒紙清潔眼罩外部<br />\n3.除眼罩口罩，再用酒精/消毒清潔劑/稀釋漂白水清潔成個眼罩"},{"pid":"82e7815ae2523620f90d3706adac55eb5c9495d7","tid":1849552,"uid":203207,"like":4,"dislike":2,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"45958a9e3058d7528af485181f9cf954f5d4b696","tid":1849552,"uid":28833,"like":9,"dislike":9,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"5b11e1c7c057c92dc2edab9ecab6636c5555cc0e","tid":1849552,"uid":203207,"like":13,"dislike":4,"score":9,"quote":{"pid":"7ccb839a2799c2e61b88a84f89426da16f693f00","tid":1849552,"uid":9394,"like":79,"dislike":6,"score":73,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2020-01-29T06:23:57.000Z","msg":"冷靜啲 <br />\n醫護確實係有需要用咁多<br />\n目標應該係逼政府拎呢堆n95派比前線醫護/救護<br />\n唔好比啲高層<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-01-29T06:25:05.000Z","msg":"如果醫護都唔夠罩 咪多個誘因/藉口罷工囉"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-29T06:26:29.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-29T06:28:23.000Z","msg":"佢地唔夠罩 會唔會返工做野阿on9?<br />\n你當人傻？"},{"pid":"fc52d55bdc9dc1a599cecd6ee4b8df94994b2af9","tid":1849552,"uid":28833,"like":1,"dislike":8,"score":-7,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2020-01-29T06:28:40.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"d3fcc325550bfcde4c1242cacb9913dcc030152a","tid":1849552,"uid":203207,"like":8,"dislike":0,